<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="81cfacaa-f9dc-4f3f-acb3-754bf8718f4a" >

    <p>We recommend using a Ryerson Purchasing Card (P-card) for payment whenever possible while Ryerson is operating essential services only. For additional information please visit the Financial Services <a href="https://www.ryerson.ca/financial-services/contact/purchasing-payment/" target="_blank">Purchasing and Payment webpage.<span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-external-link"></span><span class="sr-only">, opens in new window</span></a></p>
    





